title: Ragada
subTitle: Satya, a money-minded man, arrives in Hyderabad and starts working for a gangster, GK. However, he soon becomes the target of another gangster, Peddanna.

title: Kshatriya Ek Yodha
subTitle: An orphan pretends to love a girl in order to help his friend. However, he genuinely falls in love with her and tries to confess his feelings for her.

title: Zulm Ki Zanjeer
subTitle: Raghu returns home from the army, only to find himself at loggerheads with his estranged childhood friend, Onti, who is a dangerous gangster.

title: Mufti
subTitle: Gana, a police officer, must go undercover to find and kill Bhairathi Ranagal, a crime lord. However, when he realises that Bhairathi's intentions are good, he needs to decide his next step.

title: Khallas
subTitle: Rishi, an officer, is sent on an undercover mission to Hyderabad, where he poses as a teacher to gather intel on a gangster. However, his mission takes an unexpected turn when he falls in love with his student.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: Bhaskar and Anu are single parents with children who study in the same class. So, when their children take a liking to each other's parents, they try to bring them together to be a complete family.

title: Geetanjali 2
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: Satyabhama
subTitle: ACP Satyabhama embarks on an investigation into a missing person case, which leads her to uncover dark secrets hidden within the town. However, as she delves deeper, her past begins to haunt her.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: Surya Ka Yaarana
subTitle: A soldier going on a rescue mission, hears about his father's death by lung cancer and mournfully looks back on his memories of how he helped him in matters of love and life.

title: Ek Tha Nayak
subTitle: When a respected police officer is killed by a gangster, his younger brother decides to avenge him by hunting the man down.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Aakhri Yudh
subTitle: Babji, a loan recovery agent, decides to help Kavya when he finds her being chased by her family. However, Kavya's brother thinks that Babji and her sister are lovers and attacks his family.

title: The Masterpiece
subTitle: A young man falls in with the wrong crowd and strays from heroic deeds. However, an accidental encounter with danger forces him to change his ways.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: ACP Shiva
subTitle: An IPS officer treads the path of corruption, but when his dishonest ways prove costly, he must decide whether to seek righteous revenge.

title: Power
subTitle: A politician falls into a coma after an attack by criminals. He wakes up several years later to find his son has taken over his responsibilities. However, things are not what they seem to be.

title: Rakhwala No 1
subTitle: A man abducts his friend's girlfriend to unite the lovers but ends up kidnapping Pooja, the wrong girl. However, she heaves a sigh of relief upon escaping the clutches of her warring uncles.

title: Rakhwala No 1

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Dhruva
subTitle: A committed police officer, Dhruva, uncovers a web of organised crime headed by a scientist, Siddharth Abhimanyu. But when Dhruva tries to build a case against him, he faces many challenges.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Pichaikkaran
subTitle: A rich businessman and a poor beggar's lives intersect, showing how money influences their fates as one fights off greedy predators and the other searches for his long-lost sister.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: DD Returns
subTitle: An event manager and his friends hide the money they stole in a haunted bungalow to evade the police but when they go back to retrieve it, the ghosts force them to play a dangerous game.
